# ✈️ Faith Audisa – Personal Portfolio

Welcome to my personal portfolio website! This project highlights my passion for **aviation** and **web development**, showcasing my journey, projects, and ambitions as a **future commercial pilot and developer**.

---

## 🌟 About Me

I'm Faith Audisa — a driven student at **Kirinyaga University**, combining my love for flying with a growing expertise in tech. I dream of becoming one of the **world's top commercial pilots**, while also building creative, modern websites.

---

## 💻 Built With

- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- Font Awesome (for icons)  
- Responsive Design Techniques

